# Work Order ID: WO-APS-3-2025-06-15
# Date: 15 Jun 2025

WORK ORDER DETAILS
==================

Asset: APS-3 (Argon Purging System)
Location: Steel Melting Shop - Bay 3
Priority: HIGH
Work Type: Preventive Maintenance

SCHEDULED WORK
==============

1. Valve Inspection (V-101, V-102)
   - Check for wear and tear
   - Verify proper operation
   - Lubricate moving parts
   - Estimated Time: 2 hours

2. Sensor Calibration (P-101, T-101)
   - Calibrate pressure sensor P-101
   - Calibrate temperature sensor T-101
   - Verify alarm setpoints
   - Estimated Time: 1.5 hours

3. System Leak Test
   - Pressurize system to 2.0 bar
   - Check for leaks at all connections
   - Verify pressure holding
   - Estimated Time: 1 hour

SAFETY REQUIREMENTS
==================

- Lockout/Tagout required before work
- PPE: Safety glasses, gloves, protective clothing
- Argon ventilation must be operational
- Emergency stop accessible at all times

COMPLIANCE NOTES
===============

- PESO-8.3: Pressure vessel inspection due July 2025
- ISO 45001-8.1.2: Document all near-misses
- Previous deferred work: V-102 calibration (deferred from 01 May 2025)

